Package Main.ModelsTest

Class BrickTest

java.lang.Object
Main.ModelsTest.BrickTest
class BrickTest
extends java.lang.Object
BrickTest tests to see if the methods of Brick class which are all setters and getters are all working properly. The getters are tested first to ensure that they are working before using them to test the setters.
